{
  "stem": "734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in the [GERMAN] commanders, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] executing people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he tells the parents how proud they should be of him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There will be a new order in Europe now, he says, and that, that the fuhrer will put them on a new level, and all that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he talks about-- he talked about the fact that he couldn't-- that he was trying to contact his cousin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But apparently, he, he wasn't able to contact the cousin, Hans, who was supposed to be in a certain place, but he wasn't.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But still, he's going to write to him that they shouldn't worry, that he's in good hands, that Hans is OK, and that they shouldn't worry about him, too.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because his outfit is now doing some mopping up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Apparently, he was not-- he was not on the fighting front.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was behind the front, eliminating-- executing people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is what the job was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes, [GERMAN] commanders.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Cleaning up the area from Jews, gypsies, and undesirable elements.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, you can imagine what-- how shocked I was when I read this letter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I put it back in place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I couldn't sleep all night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for some reason, I imagined that this guy must be alive somewhere, that he might show up any minute here and see me in his bed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He might simply do away with me, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Suddenly, I got frightened over this whole aspect as to who his son is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now that the war is over, I thought maybe he's hiding someplace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe he's somewhere around the neighborhood, who knows?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't sleep all night, not a wink.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And eventually, I decided to leave as soon as I could, to leave that place.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
